            "heading": "What Are Cookies?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device (computer, tablet, or smartphone) when you visit a website. They help websites recognize your device, enhance your browsing experience, and provide relevant information.</p>",
            "page": ""
