            "heading": "Types of Cookies We Use",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h3><strong>1. Essential Cookies</strong></h3><p>These cookies are necessary for the basic functioning of our website. They allow you to browse our site, add items to your cart, and complete transactions.</p><ul><li>Examples:</li><li>Session cookies to maintain login status.</li><li>Cart cookies to remember your selected items.</li></ul><h3><strong>2. Performance Cookies</strong></h3><p>Performance cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website. They collect anonymized data about pages visited, time spent on the site, and error messages encountered.</p><ul><li>Examples:</li><li>Google Analytics cookies for website traffic analysis.</li></ul><h3><strong>3. Functionality Cookies</strong></h3><p>These cookies allow us to provide a more personalized experience by remembering your preferences, such as language settings or region selection.</p><ul><li>Examples:</li><li>Cookies to save your preferences for future visits.</li></ul><h3><strong>4. Targeting/Advertising Cookies</strong></h3><p>These cookies track your browsing activity to show you relevant ads and measure the effectiveness of our marketing campaigns. They may also be used by third-party advertisers on our site.</p><ul><li>Examples:</li><li>Facebook Pixel for retargeting.</li><li>Google Ads cookies for personalized advertising.</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
