          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Third-Party Cookies",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We may allow third-party services to place cookies on your device to provide additional functionality or advertising services. These third-party services are subject to their own privacy policies.</p><p>Examples include:</p><ul><li>Social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Pinterest.</li><li>Analytics providers like Google Analytics.</li></ul>",
